    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Immune response after a single-dose of BNT162b2 vaccine is markedly increased in subjects with previous SARS-CoV-2 infection, reaching similar IgG titers to those elicited by the full two-doses in na\u00efve cases, and increased modestly after the second dose. These data may inform the priority of the boosting dose.</jats:p>",
